            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">47.404</ph> Air freight forwarders.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d2810e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2824e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Agencies may use air freight forwarders that are engaged in international air transportation (<xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html"
                        class="- topic/xref ">49 U.S.C.1301(24)(c)</xref>) for U.S. Government-financed movements of property. The rule on disallowance of expenditures in <xref href="FAR-i1070013.dita#i1070013"
                        base="i1070013"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">47.403-3</xref>(a) applies also to the air carriers used by these international air freight forwarders.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2824e32" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Agency personnel shall inform international air freight forwarders that to facilitate prompt payments of their bills, they shall submit with their bills-</p>
					          <ol id="d2810e38" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2824e42" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                A copy of the airway bill or manifest showing the air carriers used; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2824e51" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Justification for the use of foreign-flag air carriers similar to the one shown in the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1046532.dita#i1046532"
                              base="i1046532"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.247-63</xref>, Preference for U.S.-Flag Air Carriers.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
